quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  21,30,"Mbega ntibabonye bamwe bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri yuko Amajuru n’Isi vyose vyakurikirana hanyuma turabi tandukanya hanyuma tugira mubijanye n’amazi ubuzima bw’ibintu vyose, mbega ntimwemera"
  21,31,"Dushira kw’Isi imisozi, kugira ngo ntinyigange, hanyuma dushiramwo amayira aboneka ari k’umugaragaro kugira ngo abantu batumbere inzira bacamwo"
  21,32,Hanyuma tugira Ijuru kuba ari urusenge ruzitiwe neza mugabo abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri bararengwa mukutemera n’ivyo bimenyetso vy’Imana
  21,33,"Nayo niyo yaremye Ijoro n’Umutaga hamwe n’Izuba n’Ukwezi, rero ivyo vyose bireremba mumizingi y’avyo vyagenewemwo"
  21,34,"Natwe ntitwaremye ikiremwa muntu uwariwe wese w’imbere yawe ngo abe uwuzoramba burundu, none wewe niwasandaba nibo bazoramba mubuzima bw’abo bwose"
  21,35,"Umutima w’umuntu uwariwe wese uzohonja urupfu, kandi turaba gerageza mubijanye n’ishari hamwe n’amahoro, n’iwacu mwese niyo muzosubizwa yo"
  21,36,"Bakubonye bamwe bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri nta nakimwe bakugira, ahubwo bara kwimwenyura bavuga bati:- mbega uyu niwe avuga Imana zanyu nabi kandi abo nibo bahakana Imana nyene imigisha ihagije"
  21,37,"Umuntu awariwe wese yaremwe yihutirwa, ubu vuba jewe nzobereka ibimenyetso vyanje, kuri ivyo rero ntimumputagize"
  21,38,"Bavuga bati:- iri sango twemerewe ryuguhanwa rizoba ryari nimwaba muvugisha ukuri"
  21,39,Iyo babimenya bamwe bahakana Imana yabo y’ukuri mugihe batazokingira umuriro uzoba uri mumaso yabo canke mumigongo yabo kandi batazofashwa
  21,40,Ahubwo uzoba shikira giturumbuka kandi uze ubahendeshe hanyuma ntibazo shobora kuwusubiza inyuma canke ntibazohabwa ikiringo kanaka
  21,41,"Ntankeka barakengereye intumwa z’Imana zabayeho aho hambere yabo, rero bamwe bakengereye izo ntumwa z’Imana muribo barashikiwe nivyo bahora bakengera ko"